              "chord": "",
              "text": "Flesh He became, the first God-man,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "His pleasure that I God may be:"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "In life and nature I’m God’s kind,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Though Godhead’s His exclusively."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "His attributes my virtues are;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "His glorious image shines through me."
            }
          ]
        },
